## Build Instructions

1. **Clone the Repository**:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/geant4-proton-collision.git
   cd geant4-proton-collision
   ```
2. **Create a Build Directory**:
     ```bash
     mkdir build
     cd build
     ```
3. **Build the Program**:
    ```bash
    cmake ..
    make
    ```
4. **Running the Simulation**:
    ```bash
    ./sim
    ```
